Product Name (Working Title)

QuoteCraft – Custom Quotation & RFQ Builder

1️⃣ Product Overview

QuoteCraft is a browser-based tool that allows businesses to create fully customizable quotations, RFQs, and proforma invoices with branded layouts and downloadable PDF output — without requiring login or database storage in Version 1.

The product focuses on:

Fast document generation

Full visual customization

Clean professional PDF output

Zero backend complexity

2️⃣ Problem Statement

Small and mid-size businesses:

Use MS Word manually

Re-edit the same format repeatedly

Struggle with branding consistency

Waste time formatting tables

Generate low-quality PDFs

There is no simple, customizable, instant quotation builder without heavy SaaS complexity.

3️⃣ Goals (V1)
Primary Goals

Allow users to create professional quotations in under 5 minutes

Allow full layout customization

Generate high-quality downloadable PDF

Run fully frontend (no backend)

Non-Goals (V1)

No user accounts

No database storage

No multi-user

No document history

No online sharing links

