5️⃣ Core Features (MVP)
🔹 5.1 Branding Customization Module
Purpose

Allow user to visually brand the quotation.

Functional Requirements

User can:

Upload logo (PNG, JPG, SVG)

Choose primary color

Choose secondary color

Choose font (Google Fonts dropdown)

Select layout template (3 options)

System Behavior

Branding changes update live preview instantly

Branding applied to generated PDF

Store branding in local state

Optionally persist in localStorage

